
Install ibus-vadan
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Run "python setup.py -install" as root
It will install 'ibus-vadan'.

But you need an active 'ibus' instance to use 'ibus-vadan'.
You can start 'ibus' by running "ibus-daemon".
Then you have to edit ibus preferences and add 'ibus-vadan' as default
	input method
Default shortcut key combination for ibus is Ctrl+Space. you can switch between
	your default keyboard layout and 'ibus-vadan' by using above shortcut key.

================================================================================


Test ibus-vadan
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

First change directory to 'test' directory.
Start ibus-daemon if it not started.
Execute test.py.
Switch to 'ibus-vadan' input method.


